  "text": "REGD NO D. L- 33004/99 The Gazette of India EXTRAORDINARY PART III—Section 4 PUBLISHED BY AUTHORITY No. 1] NEW DELHI, TUESDAY, JANUARY 2, 2001/PAUSA 12, 1922 SMALL INDUSTRIES DEVELOPMENT BANK OF INDIA CORRIGENDUM New Delhi, the 22nd December, 2000 Small Industries Development Bank of India General Regulations, 2000 Referring to the Small Industries Development Bank of India notification published in the Gazette of India (Extraordinary) Part III Section IV issue number 141 dated November 13, 2000 on page 88, after sub-regulation (5) of regulation 64 and before sub-regulation (1) of regulation 65 the following shall be read 65 Directors to be elected at general meetings.\" S C GARG General Manager (Legal) [ ADVT /III/lV/139/24/Exty] 14 G I / 2 0 0 1 Printed by the Manager Govt of Indin Press Ring Road Mayapuri Now Delhi-110064 and Published by the Controller of Publications Delhi-110054 -- 1 of 2 -- -- 2 of 2 --",
